    },
    {
      "id": "6a10bc2400000000009f992e",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/f992e2a1464c471019393a71e45a552a]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779481636,
      "updated": 1779481702
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10bc6600000000009f992f",
      "text": "[ふーこ.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779481702,
      "updated": 1779481718
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10bc8b00000000009f9930",
      "text": "思いついたことを脈絡もなく書くエリア（引用禁止）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779481739,
      "updated": 1779482011
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10bcb700000000009f9931",
      "text": "　造語の逆で、「いろんな用語を整理してみると、みんな一つの同じことを指しているようだ」みたいなのなんていうのだろう？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779481784,
      "updated": 1779483441
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10c2e300000000003f98ee",
      "text": "　　この用語はいらないよね、みたいな感じ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779483363,
      "updated": 1779483398
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10c30600000000003f98ef",
      "text": "　　適切な用語への置き換え",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779483398,
      "updated": 1779483412
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10bd7900000000009f9933",
      "text": "　　[概念整理]？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779481977,
      "updated": 1779519934
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10c22e00000000003f98ec",
      "text": "　　なんか新しいことを言ってるようだけど、調べてみたら昔のアレを同じ、みたいな",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779483182,
      "updated": 1779483270
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10c28700000000003f98ed",
      "text": "　　　[文脈]をよく理解できていないのではないかと悩むやつ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779483272,
      "updated": 1779519971
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1151c500000000004bd293",
      "text": "　　　むしろ文脈をよく理解することが重要なやつ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779519941,
      "updated": 1779519998
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10bcb800000000009f9932",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779481784,
      "updated": 1779481784
    },
    {
      "id": "6a11517f00000000004bd292",
      "text": "[[ちゃっぴー.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779519871,
      "updated": 1779519887
    },
    {
      "id": "6a11512e0000000000730387",
      "text": " どういう使いみちがあるだろう？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779519791,
      "updated": 1779525002
    },
    {
      "id": "6a116d34000000000033433b",
      "text": "[[deck-めざせ井戸端マスター.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779526964,
      "updated": 1779526979
    },
    {
      "id": "6a11656d000000000033433a",
      "text": " こんなページがあったのか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779524973,
      "updated": 1779527009
    },
    {
      "id": "6a116d4c000000000033433c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
